How to reject auto update of Adobe Reader DC

Disable the task scheduler libraries "Adobe Acrobat Update Task".
Disable the services "Adobe Acrobat Update Service".

Set the registry HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Wow6432Node\Adobe\Adobe ARM\Legacy\Reader\{AC76BA86-7AD7-1041-7B44-AC0F074E4100}\Mode to 0.
Make a registry HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Adobe\Acrobat Reader\DC\FeatureLockDown\bUpdater and set it to 0.
